# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# BACKEND ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── Node Environment ──────────────────────────────
NODE_ENV=development
PORT=3000
LOG_LEVEL=debug

# ── Database ───────────────────────────────────────
MONGODB_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017/socialhub
MONGODB_POOL_SIZE=10
MONGODB_MAX_RETRIES=5

# ── Redis (Caching & Sessions) ────────────────────
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379
REDIS_DB=0
REDIS_PASSWORD=your_redis_password

# ── JWT Secrets ────────────────────────────────────
JWT_SECRET=your_super_secret_jwt_key_min_32_chars
REFRESH_TOKEN_SECRET=your_refresh_token_secret_min_32_chars
JWT_EXPIRY=1h
REFRESH_TOKEN_EXPIRY=7d

# ── Email Configuration ───────────────────────────
EMAIL_SERVICE=gmail
EMAIL_USER=your_email@gmail.com
EMAIL_PASS=your_app_password_here
EMAIL_FROM=noreply@socialhub.app
EMAIL_DOMAIN=socialhub.app

# ── Frontend URLs ──────────────────────────────────
FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:3001
FRONTEND_URL_PROD=https://app.socialhub.app

# ── OAuth Configuration ────────────────────────────
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your_google_client_id
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=your_google_client_secret
GOOGLE_CALLBACK_URL=http://localhost:3000/api/auth/oauth/google/callback

FACEBOOK_APP_ID=your_facebook_app_id
FACEBOOK_APP_SECRET=your_facebook_app_secret
FACEBOOK_CALLBACK_URL=http://localhost:3000/api/auth/oauth/facebook/callback

LINKEDIN_CLIENT_ID=your_linkedin_client_id
LINKEDIN_CLIENT_SECRET=your_linkedin_client_secret
LINKEDIN_CALLBACK_URL=http://localhost:3000/api/auth/oauth/linkedin/callback

# ── Social Media APIs ──────────────────────────────
# Instagram Graph API
INSTAGRAM_BUSINESS_ACCOUNT_ID=your_instagram_account_id
INSTAGRAM_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_instagram_access_token

# Twitter API
TWITTER_API_KEY=your_twitter_api_key
TWITTER_API_SECRET=your_twitter_api_secret
TWITTER_BEARER_TOKEN=your_twitter_bearer_token

# Facebook Graph API
FACEBOOK_PAGE_ID=your_facebook_page_id
FACEBOOK_PAGE_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_facebook_access_token

# LinkedIn API
LINKEDIN_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_linkedin_access_token

# ── Cloud Storage ──────────────────────────────────
AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=your_aws_access_key
AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=your_aws_secret_key
AWS_REGION=ap-southeast-1
AWS_S3_BUCKET=socialhub-uploads
AWS_S3_ENDPOINT=https://s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com

# ── Analytics & Monitoring ────────────────────────
SENTRY_DSN=https://your_sentry_dsn
SENTRY_ENVIRONMENT=development
SENTRY_TRACE_SAMPLE_RATE=0.5

# ── Rate Limiting ──────────────────────────────────
RATE_LIMIT_WINDOW_MS=900000  # 15 minutes
RATE_LIMIT_MAX_REQUESTS=100

# ── Stripe (Billing) ───────────────────────────────
STRIPE_PUBLIC_KEY=pk_test_your_stripe_public_key
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_your_stripe_secret_key
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_your_webhook_secret

# ── CORS & Security ───────────────────────────────
CORS_ORIGIN=http://localhost:3001,https://app.socialhub.app
CORS_CREDENTIALS=true

# API Rate Limiting
API_RATE_LIMIT_ENABLED=true
API_RATE_LIMIT_WINDOW=900000
API_RATE_LIMIT_MAX=100

# ── Features ───────────────────────────────────────
FEATURE_2FA_ENABLED=true
FEATURE_COLLABORATION_ENABLED=true
FEATURE_ADVANCED_ANALYTICS=true
FEATURE_SOCIAL_LISTENING=false
FEATURE_INFLUENCER_DISCOVERY=false
FEATURE_AI_OPTIMIZATION=true

# ── Logging ────────────────────────────────────────
LOG_FORMAT=json
LOG_DIR=./logs
LOG_MAX_SIZE=10m
LOG_MAX_FILES=14

# ── Security Headers ──────────────────────────────
HSTS_MAX_AGE=31536000
HSTS_INCLUDE_SUBDOMAINS=true
HSTS_PRELOAD=true

# ── Admin Settings ────────────────────────────────
ADMIN_EMAIL=admin@socialhub.app
SUPPORT_EMAIL=support@socialhub.app

# ── Webhook URLs ──────────────────────────────────
INSTAGRAM_WEBHOOK_URL=https://api.socialhub.app/webhooks/instagram
FACEBOOK_WEBHOOK_URL=https://api.socialhub.app/webhooks/facebook
TWITTER_WEBHOOK_URL=https://api.socialhub.app/webhooks/twitter

# ── Cache Settings ────────────────────────────────
CACHE_TTL=3600
CACHE_ENABLED=true
CACHE_TYPE=redis  # 'redis', 'memory'
